I have never seen a more terrifying and violating app. Before I had ever put in personal info into the app, a squad of orange Cheetos, ritz crackers, and oranges had surrounded my house chanting in Latin and wearing orange capes.  For the first few days all they did was chant, hold hands, and walk around in rings. But then on the fourth day things changed. I watched in horror from my window as they started to move closer in a tightening ring around my house almost like a noose. Step by step. Then they stopped and started playing a song that will haunt me forever: the star spangled banner in G minor. But the notes were wrong and it carried an eerie sense of doom as they played their trumpets like phantoms. This went on for another day. Then their hypnotic song started brainwashing my neighbors and I could only watch, terrified, as they emerged from their homes, their skin turning to orange as their shapes changed to match their Cheeto, ritz cracker, and orange brethren. They walked at first but then they were sprinting toward my house at full speed before banging on my windows untill they broke. Then all of them, my brainwashed neighbors AND the cult started attacking me and coming in through the windows. There were hundreds of them and I had to hide in my car as they rocked it back and forth before flipping it over with me still inside. For hours I prayed and sobbed and hoped with every bone in my body to make it out alive. And then I heard a loud and shrill whistle and in unison they all turned toward the sound before sprinting and disappearing into the woods behind my house. I have had no problems since but I am planning on moving out of state after this incident. Very disappointing. -1000000000000/10
attributes.title: Attacked by cult
